name: Craziness Spirals I
description:
"The way it feels
We keep moving on"


Raw material/frames taken from the music video of the Brazilian band Deafkids "Espirais da Loucura" which I produced entirely from 0. 
It was originally released by Neurosis's record label Neurot Recordings in 2019.


Dimensions: 1490 × 1080

(Sony Trinitron + VHS + Analog Circuit Bent equipment + Sony Alpha)
